<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Indifferent2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Indifferent,</orth> adv. pretty, rather, somewhat: <cit><quote>I'll tell you news i. good for either,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.181" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 181</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>it does i. well,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 1.3.143" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 3, 143</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>two lips i. red,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.265" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 265</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Harry of Monmouth's life is come after it i. well,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.34" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 34</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he'll fight i. well,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.242" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 242</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I am i. honest,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.123" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 1, 123</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>it is i. cold,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.100" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 100</bibl></cit>.
